cell.p:
One member of high standing and honor who shall be the
                                    Provisional President of the Republic and be selected from the
                                    Constitutionalists;

row.cell:
The Board of Government will be requested to devote special
                                attention to the following problems: 

The agrarian question;

Electoral legislation;

Laws of compulsory primary education and agricultural
                                        education;

Organization of the necessary schools and experimental
                                        institutions.
